                      <strong>Unlock New Slots:</strong> Upgrades provide additional tool slots
                    </div>
                  </li>
                  <li class="flex items-start">
                    <span class="text-indigo-400 mr-3 mt-1">⚡</span>
                    <div>
                      <strong>Enhanced Abilities:</strong> Unlock new capabilities and effects
                    </div>
                  </li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-indigo-400 mb-6">Acquisition Methods</h3>
              <ul class="space-y-4 text-gray-300">
